            <h1>Installation Guide</h1>
            <p>Once a user is registered with the WSO2 Gadget Server he/she can sign in to the user area. The portal
                user area
                can be easily customized with user's preferences. He/She can add remove new gadgets, can browse the
                gadget repository,can search for gadgets in the gadget repository based on gadget names,
                can change the gadget layout, copy gadgets, add new tabs and clone current tabs. The users can also add
                any other gadget which are hosted elsewhere
                to the portal via add by url feature. All the features are available for the signed in user, and
                permissions can be modified by the administrators.
